<h3>Website</h3>
<p>This website (<a href="http://www.walkercms.net" title="WalkerCMS Home">WalkerCMS.net</a>) runs on
   WalkerCMS (yes, we
   <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Eating_your_own_dog_food" title="Dogfooding definitions">dogfood</a>).
   However, the design template was created by <a href="http://www.styleshout.com/" title="Styleshout">Styleshout</a>,
   though we modified it to fit our particular needs. The design template is licensed under the
   <a href="http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/2.5/">Creative Commons Attribution 2.5 License</a>.</p>
